longDescription.en:
Through an editorial panorama of the comic book, manga and comic book industry, we invite you to come and listen to the suggestions of Antoine and Stéphane, booksellers at Momie Grenoble in order to start again with reading tracks, ideas for your purchases and tips for educating your library users.
Speakers: Antoine and Stéphane, booksellers at Momie Grenoble
From 1pm to 5pm:
- Presentation of comics and graphic novels;
- Presentation of comics
- Presentation of mangas and manhuas;
From 5pm to 6pm:
- On-site consultation of works;
